s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔吸取教訓無野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a7dd7ea585cd4e868d205c98f01905a96ed14f","tid":411500,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠炒賣發達既吸血鬼死不足惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7afa1ad65436c355a06e906af96d099c880ddbd8","tid":411500,"uid":7805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/140357_d5c2fad03c578ffef2e97bee78fbc3a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F140357_d5c2fad03c578ffef2e97bee78fbc3a1.jpg&h=1e1f7721&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}